               <p>I live in <placeName id="t17900424-10-crimeloc59">Aldersgate-street, at the Aldersgate coffee-house</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17900424-10-crimeloc59" type="placeName" value="Aldersgate-street, at the Aldersgate coffee-house"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17900424-10-crimeloc59" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900424-10-off57 t17900424-10-crimeloc59"></join>. On Saturday, the 3d of April, the prisoner was assisting my people in the business in the kitchen; he was an occasional assistant to my servants; on Sunday, I missed one spoon, in the morning, when I looked over them; my servants made enquiry, and applied to the constable; and the beadle came and informed me my spoon was at the pawn-broker's.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17900424-10-person105">
                  MARY
                   WHITE
               <interp inst="t17900424-10-person105" type="surname" value="WHITE"></interp>
